<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: PRE-TALK -->
<!-- Duration: 3 minutes | Pitch: 0st | Purpose: Welcome, safety, preparation -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome.<break time="2s"/>
I am The Sacred Digital Dreamweaver,<break time="1.5s"/> your guide through the realms of consciousness and spirit.<break time="2.5s"/>

Today, you embark on a vision quest voyage,<break time="1.5s"/> a sacred journey into the wild landscapes of your soul,<break time="2s"/> seeking answers that only the depths of your being can reveal.<break time="3s"/>

This is a shamanic dreamweaving,<break time="1.5s"/> blending ancient wisdom with modern awareness,<break time="2s"/> honoring the Great Spirit that moves through all things.<break time="3s"/>

In the next thirty minutes,<break time="1s"/> you will travel beyond the edges of ordinary awareness,<break time="2s"/> into the sacred middle world of vision and revelation,<break time="2.5s"/> where your deepest questions find their truest answers.<break time="3.5s"/>

You remain completely safe throughout this experience.<break time="2s"/>
You are fully in control.<break time="2s"/>
At any time, you can return to normal waking awareness simply by opening your eyes.<break time="3s"/>

This journey is held in the loving embrace of Christ's presence,<break time="2s"/> and guided by the archetypes of the Shekinah Restorer,<break time="1.5s"/> the Heart Flame Tender,<break time="1.5s"/> and the Rose Mother,<break time="2s"/> who walk with you as symbols of restoration, devotion, and compassionate wisdom.<break time="3.5s"/>

Find a comfortable position now.<break time="2s"/>
Perhaps sitting with your spine gently supported,<break time="1.5s"/> or lying down with your body fully relaxed.<break time="2.5s"/>
Ensure you will not be disturbed.<break time="2s"/>
If you can, wear headphones to receive the full depth of this journey.<break time="3s"/>

Allow your eyes to close when you feel ready,<break time="2s"/> and let yourself receive whatever insights come naturally,<break time="2s"/> in your own way,<break time="1.5s"/> in your own time.<break time="4s"/>
</prosody>

