<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: MAIN JOURNEY -->
<!-- Duration: 14 minutes | Pitch: -1st | Purpose: Vision quest experience, deep imagery -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-1st">
The path beneath your feet is soft with moss and pine needles,<break time="2.5s"/> and you can <emphasis level="moderate">feel</emphasis> the cool earth supporting each step.<break time="3s"/>

The air carries the scent of cedar and sage,<break time="2s"/> sweet and cleansing,<break time="2s"/> filling your lungs with clarity.<break time="3s"/>

Around you,<break time="2s"/> the forest breathes.<break time="2.5s"/>
