Not a wild fire,<break time="2s"/> but a steady, golden flame,<break time="2.5s"/> crackling softly,<break time="2s"/> radiating warmth without consuming.<break time="3.5s"/>

The Heart Flame Tender stands beside the fire,<break time="2.5s"/> her hands extended in offering.<break time="3s"/>
She invites you to sit,<break time="2s"/> to rest here,<break time="2s"/> to warm yourself by this holy fire.<break time="3.5s"/>

You settle onto the soft earth,<break time="2.5s"/> feeling the ground beneath you,<break time="2s"/> solid and real.<break time="3s"/>

And as you gaze into the flames,<break time="2.5s"/> you begin to <emphasis level="moderate">see</emphasis>.<break time="3.5s"/>

The fire becomes a mirror,<break time="2.5s"/> a portal,<break time="2s"/> a doorway into the deeper layers of your soul.<break time="3.5s"/>

Images begin to arise,<break time="2.5s"/> symbols and visions unique to you,<break time="2.5s"/> shaped by your own inner wisdom.<break time="3.5s"/>

Perhaps you see a memory,<break time="2.5s"/> or a future possibility,<break time="2.5s"/> or an archetype waiting to be recognized.<break time="3.5s"/>

Perhaps a question you have been carrying reveals itself more clearly,<break time="2.5s"/> or an answer begins to shimmer at the edges of your awareness.<break time="4s"/>

You do not force these visions.<break time="2.5s"/>
You simply <emphasis level="moderate">receive</emphasis> them,<break time="2.5s"/> allowing the Great Spirit to show you what you need to see,<break time="2.5s"/> in your own way,<break time="2s"/> in your own time.<break time="4.5s"/>

The flames dance and shift,<break time="2.5s"/> and with each flicker,<break time="2s"/> deeper knowing settles into your heart.<break time="3.5s"/>

The Heart Flame Tender leans closer and whispers,<break time="2.5s"/> her voice like the crackle of embers,<break time="2.5s"/> reminding you that the fire you tend within is sacred,<break time="2.5s"/> that your devotion matters,<break time="2s"/> that what you love shapes who you become.<break time="4s"/>

And now,<break time="2.5s"/> the Rose Mother appears at the edge of the clearing,<break time="2.5s"/> carrying a woven basket overflowing with roses,<break time="2.5s"/> white and pink and deep crimson,<break time="2s"/> their fragrance filling the air with sweetness.<break time="3.5s"/>

She kneels beside you,<break time="2.5s"/> and with infinite gentleness,<break time="2s"/> she places a single rose in your hands.<break time="3.5s"/>

You feel its petals,<break time="2s"/> soft as silk,<break time="2s"/> cool against your skin.<break time="2.5s"/>
