The guides stand with you,<break time="2.5s"/> honoring this revelation,<break time="2.5s"/> and the fire behind you glows warmer,<break time="2.5s"/> as if blessing what has been seen.<break time="4s"/>

You place your rose gently on the altar,<break time="2.5s"/> an offering of gratitude,<break time="2.5s"/> and you turn to face the path once more.<break time="3.5s"/>

It is time to return,<break time="2.5s"/> carrying with you all that you have received.<break time="4s"/>
